---
/**
 * UpsellMedicos.astro — bloco de upsell pro plano completo Selvia
 *
 * Usado na LP do Agendamento de Plantão (gratuito) pra conduzir pro plano
 * completo de médicos. Mostra os principais benefícios da modalidade paga
 * e o ponto de entrada (que é a home, já que médicos não tem LP separada).
 *
 * Visual: bloco verde escuro tipo CTA Final, mas com lista de features
 * incluídas no plano completo.
 */
---

<section class="upsell-medicos">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="upsell-medicos-block">
      <span class="upsell-medicos-eyebrow">Quer mais que agendamento?</span>
      <h2 class="upsell-medicos-title">Conheça a Selvia completa pra médicos.</h2>
      <p class="upsell-medicos-sub">
        Além do agendamento de plantão gratuito, a Selvia cuida de toda a
        contabilidade do médico PJ. Tudo no mesmo WhatsApp.
      </p>

      <ul class="upsell-medicos-list">
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Abertura do CNPJ no enquadramento certo
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Emissão de nota fiscal direto no WhatsApp
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Pagamento automático dos impostos (DAS, ISS, IR)
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Receita Saúde emitida pra cada atendimento particular
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Resumo financeiro mensal com impostos calculados
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          Atendimento humano 24h pelo WhatsApp
        </li>
      </ul>

      <a href="/" class="upsell-medicos-btn">
        Ver plano completo para médicos
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .upsell-medicos {
    padding: 56px 0;
    background: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-block {
    background: var(--c-green-dark);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 56px 48px;
    color: var(--c-offwhite);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-block::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(105,228,112,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .upsell-medicos-block > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--c-green-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-title {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--c-offwhite);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.6px;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-sub {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(249,249,249,0.78);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .upsell-medicos-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(249,249,249,0.92);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .upsell-medicos-list svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--c-green-light);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .upsell-medicos-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    background: var(--c-green-light);
    color: var(--c-green-dark);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(105,228,112,0.25);
  }
  .upsell-medicos-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(105,228,112,0.4);
    background: #7BEE82;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .upsell-medicos-block {
      padding: 40px 28px;
    }
    .upsell-medicos-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
